snippet.title: Garden Rush: Official Release Trailer.
snippet.description:
Let the rushing: commence.

Garden Rush is a PVZ2 mod that defines itself on being interesting, unique and a change of pace from your traditional Plants VS Zombies 2 mod. We have Abilities, Hero Plants and all sorts of other minor changes you won't see in another mod. This is a mod I have worked on for a long time now, over a year now, and this CERTAINLY won't be the last you'll see of it! I hope you look forward to it as much as I did working on it. 

Download Link:https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1u0rwqBS-b4QC5vYS6AGg-4IzK9tNYYkv?usp=drive_link for Drive
and
https://mega.nz/folder/8rdmxajL#7HwFXjq00t899Cb2mQGZyw for Mega
Discord for both this mod and my channel: https://discord.gg/HSfyBnx

Hey! I'm creeps, a guy on YouTube who does things on YouTube. I mostly make Video Essays on Plants Vs. Zombies 2. Or Plants Vs Zombies. or whatever. Still, these videos tend to go in depth on plants, mechanics or other features you may not realise. I also stream sometimes. And I also play a lot of PVZ2 mods on those streams, usually really cool ones that are awesome and good. Hope you stick around!
